  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 1st level, you have become a force to be reckoned with on the battlefield. You gain a number of d4's called \"Ki Dice\" that you can spend while in combat. You have a number of these dice equal to your Proficiency modifier. You regain all expended Ki Dice at the end of a short rest. At 3rd level, your Ki Dice increases to a d6, at 7th level it becomes a d8, at 11th level it becomes a d10, and at 18th it becomes a d12.</p>",
